overview: She came to Hollywood like so many beautiful girls: beautiful, ripe, voluptuous, oversexed and willing to do anything to become a star. And like so many before her, she knew that she might have to use her fabulous body to get into that inner circle of international stardom. She was right. Fortunately, for Suzie, she loved every lurid moment of the wildest, wickedest, kinkiest sex with the most turned on people. So get ready for an opening night spectacular, we'll show you every blatantly erotic moment!
title: Suzie Superstar 3
